### Test MCP HTTP Server - Send Greeting Email

### 1. Send a greeting email (successful case)
POST http://localhost:8082/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "send_greeting_email",
    "arguments": {
      "toEmail": "test@example.com",
      "greetingText": "Hello! This is a test greeting from the MCP HTTP server. Have a wonderful day!"
    }
  }
}

